<i>noun</i>: 풀밭 [풀받], 풀 [풀], 잔디 [잔디] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풀밭 [풀받]</dt><br>
<dd>grass; meadow</dd><br>
<dd>풀이 많이 난 땅.</dd><br>
<dd>A piece of land that is full of grass.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>풀 [풀]</dt><br>
<dd>grass; herb; weed</dd><br>
<dd>줄기가 연하고, 대개 한 해를 지내면 죽는 식물.</dd><br>
<dd>A plant with a tender stem that usually dies after one year.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>잔디 [잔디]</dt><br>
<dd>turf; sod; grass</dd><br>
<dd>정원, 공원, 골프장 등에 심는 잎이 짧고 가늘며, 촘촘하게 자라는 풀.</dd><br>
<dd>Grass that have short, narrow leaves, grow close together, and are planted in a garden, park, golf links, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>